    title: 'Event Quest "Valley of Light" Coming Soon',
    body: '<section>\n<div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/db08e693eb7fbb4f07cd7389345c6103db7f6c16e0d76bb8802510c2329b3c7d">\n</div><p>\n\nHello, and thank you for playing NieR Re[in]carnation.<br />\n\nThis is a message from the management team.<br /><br />\nThe Event Quest <span class="text-red">"Record: Valley of Light"</span> will be available Mar. 6 18:00 PST.\n</p>\n</section><section>\n<h3>Duration</h3>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 6 18:00 - 19 17:59 PST\n</div>\n</section><section>\n\n<h3>How to Play Event Quests</h3><div class="info-largeimage">\n<img src="/images/en/operations/banner/78ac32559f0ca700f4c4a4bcd06d39133821f450722d83ce08ce4e5d35243455">\n</div>\n\n<p>\nAs you proceed through the quests, you will be able to read an <span class="text-red">event-exclusive story</span>.<br />\nSave up the <span class="text-red">Valley of Light Medals</span> you receive for completing quests to trade in at the <span class="text-red">Valley of Light Medal Exchange</span> for an event-exclusive character, as well as enhancements and other items.<br />\n<br />\nThe more difficult the quest, the more Valley of Light Medals you will earn as a reward.<br />\nAdditionally, using certain characters, costumes, or weapons in "Record: Valley of Light" will grant you a <span class="text-red">quest bonus</span> that will allow you to play the event quest more efficiently.<br />\n<br />\nNote: This event quest will be unlocked upon completing Main Quest Ch. 2.<br />\nNote: Check the event notice for more details about the quest bonus.\n</p><br />\n<h4>Record: Valley of Light Medal Exchange Duration</h4>\n<div class="holding-period">\nMar. 6 18:00 - 21 17:59 PST\n</div>\n</section><section> \n <h3>\n  Notes\n  </h3>  <div class="attention_content">\n  <ul>\n  <li>\n  Event periods and content are subject to change without notice.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  Illustrations shown in notices, etc. may differ from those in-game.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  You cannot have more than one character with same name in the same deck.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  <span class="text-red">You will no longer be able to exchange medals</span> once the exchange period has passed.\n  </li>\n  <li>\n  Event-specific medals are only redeemable for a limited time and <span class="text-red">cannot be carried over to the next event.</li> \n <li> \n  This event may return in the future.\n  </li>\n  </ul>\n  </div>\n</section><br />\n\n<section>\n\n<p>\n\nThank you very much for your ongoing support for NieR Re[in]carnation.\n\n</p>\n\n</section>',
